name: The Circle France
overview: Status and strategy collide in this social media competition where online players flirt, befriend and catfish their way toward 100,000 euros.

episodes.name: Hello Circle
episodes.overview: With 100,000 euros on the line, players set out to build the perfect social media profile — knowing every tiny detail could affect their standing.

episodes.name: Blocked
episodes.overview: Before the first two influencers can decide which player to block, a game of Agree or Disagree? puts everyone in the hot seat.

episodes.name: #cgolri
episodes.overview: A newcomer changes the chemistry, a game tests players' movie knowledge, and a hashtag raises major doubts about someone's identity.

episodes.name: The Rocking Grandmothers
episodes.overview: Two influencers square off in a delicate negotiation. The grandmas bring another player to tears. New profile photos pump up the intrigue.

episodes.name: #TeamWinner
episodes.overview: Newbie Nelia wastes no time rocking the boat. When players have to tag each other in memes, a former influencer becomes a favorite target.

episodes.name: Knocked Out
episodes.overview: A rule change turns the elimination process into a showdown between two clans. Players break out their best handwriting to welcome a new contender.

episodes.name: Alliances
episodes.overview: One faker sets out to unmask another, a pajama party turns awkward, and #TeamWinner invites a fourth player into the fold.

episodes.name: The Last 8
episodes.overview: After a tricky elimination round, one player vows to avenge a friend. A pastry challenge pushes the group way out of their comfort zone.

episodes.name: The Super Influencer
episodes.overview: The Circle's first superinfluencer weighs a crucial decision. As rivals race to win over Virginie, a truth-telling game stirs up strong feelings.

episodes.name: The Betrayal
episodes.overview: Another rule change leaves some players regretting their bold behavior. A blocked player makes one last bid to turn allies against each other.

episodes.name: No Filter
episodes.overview: With the finals in sight, players switch strategies and scramble to get close to the influencers. Sparks fly during an anonymous chat.

episodes.name: The Finale
episodes.overview: Emotions run high and surprises abound as the remaining players rank each other one last time — and finally meet face to face.
